{"tid":1170833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】被WiFi聯盟拒門外 美制裁下再遭重挫","createTime":"2019-05-25T09:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T13:41:50.000Z","uid":10717,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5f520430e1b8253302b15d36e784926bbc9418","tid":1170833,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"美國日前宣佈對中國電訊製造商華為的出口禁令，越來越多重要企業紛紛響應。繼制定SD記憶卡標準的SD協會（The SD Association）將華為從該組織的名單上刪除後，無線網絡認證組織Wi-Fi聯盟（Wi-Fi Alliance）表示，基於特朗普政府最近對華為的技術禁令要求，「暫時限制」華為在該組織的參與活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國科技網站CNET說，華為仍然可以使用目前Wi-Fi和SD記憶卡的相關技術，但可能失去了未來參與新標準制訂的決策權。<br />\n另外，制訂半導體產品標準的組織JEDEC透露，華為「自願」退出了該組織。JEDEC說，華為5月17日表示，決定中止在JEDEC的成員身份，直到美國政府施加的限制解除為止。<br />\n相關新聞：【華為危機】傳向多間銀行尋求$78億離岸貸款 美國禁令後首次<br />\n<br />\n華為在一份聲明中說：「華為重視與全球所有合作夥伴和協會的關係，瞭解他們所處的困境。我們希望這種情況能夠得到解決，並在努力尋找最佳解決方案」。<br />\n被排除在行業標準制定組織之外可能為華為的未來發展帶來衝擊。專家表示，華為仍然有能力生產晶元和產品，但由於缺少影響國際標準制定的能力，未來公司的國際競爭力將受挫。"},{"pid":"516f63a5451f8d77e9f11526efd579de8f183fb9","tid":1170833,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"不嬲共產黨鐘意有自己一套標準<br />\n唔柒理世界常規,不過其實都係抄人<br />\n而家自食其果,得嘗所願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd91b65e0b268d83b893538c7fa06b0ebb3513bc","tid":1170833,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf5df84b73ad1da60d43a028e96ba22b95039d2","tid":1170833,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"用算盤"},{"pid":"38c678e9c05827e632c7383a3a8016371160872e","tid":1170833,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:06:36.000Z","msg":"收皮了"},{"pid":"72fa17b5b3221960069309de485b45a9b0a878b3","tid":1170833,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:45:27.000Z","msg":"點解習仔唔借錢俾華為，大撒幣成千億都唔借幾拾億俾非非？"},{"pid":"4892604c394c1d36fa7c6fbacd79a73733039b56","tid":1170833,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"華為又可以自主研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282ab7bd4aa3a6dcad063a01fae63f3c535e9b3d","tid":1170833,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:48:30.000Z","msg":"唔打喇唔打喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774a526e08af3861a0315e771da6e808f8077918","tid":1170833,"uid":3704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"下個到Bluetooth<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e03235cde1e6c23f0048b5e5fc521e4b975d051","tid":1170833,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:21:50.000Z","msg":"華為好撚巴閉架，可能幾年前已經硏發左自家wifi呢"},{"pid":"a88cf419d6cba00688b50ea5bcb7bdf30c18c10b","tid":1170833,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又贏"},{"pid":"b71233b9a139c1022ae24303dbb9494031dbcace","tid":1170833,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774a526e08af3861a0315e771da6e808f8077918","tid":1170833,"uid":3704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"下個到Bluetooth<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.